== Epistaxis
=== Causes
- *Local:* trauma (nose-picking)(*children*), infection, neoplasm, deviation septum, dry climate.
- *Systemic:* hypertension(*adult*), blood dyscrasias, liver disease, anticoagulant therapy.
=== Management
