= Tongue
== Ulcer on Tongue
_A 45 years old female presented with ulcer in the right margin of tongue. She had H/O taking betel leaf and tobacco chewing._ 
=== Diagnosis
Squamous Cell Carcinoma (commonly lateral border).  
=== Investigation
Biopsy, chest X-ray, LFTs (for metastasis).  
=== Treatment
Wide local excision/glossectomy + neck dissection ± radiotherapy.